Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.36,0:00:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.91,0:00:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.58,0:00:43.16,Default_P,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要緊吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.56,0:00:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不好意思 我太慌張了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.09,0:00:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,545)}由於她家離事務所很遠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.09,0:00:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以每天都像這樣很早就坐電車上班
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.73,0:01:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上班途中不可缺少的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.90,0:01:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,450)}音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.70,0:01:24.70,Default_P,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到事務所大概要多長時間？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.45,0:01:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…大約是兩個小時吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.21,0:01:30.21,Default_P,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天來回是不是很累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.73,0:01:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 不過在電車裡聽聽音樂 看看試鏡的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間很快就過去了 所以我不在意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.65,0:01:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.44,0:01:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安 春香
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:49.14,Default_P,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在看什麼呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.45,0:01:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.16,0:01:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像我的作風嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.19,0:01:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的秘密 其實我還是挺喜歡這種東西的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.11,0:02:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一共212日元
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.29,0:02:08.25,Default_P,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說菊池小姐有很多女性Fans…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.66,0:02:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這樣我並不討厭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.17,0:02:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但果然還是希望能被普通男孩子關注
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.34,0:02:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}藝人事務所 765 Production
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.78,0:02:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電梯什麼時候才能修好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.14,0:02:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 正好當做運動嘛 有什麼不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.58,0:02:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 這裡就是我們的事務所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.87,0:02:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一～二 歡迎來到765PRO
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.36,0:02:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60\pos(658,525)}從今以後就是{\fs90}她們{\fs60\1c&H1901E1&}的{\r}{\fs90}開始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.04,0:02:48.80,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,450)\fs90\pos(640,510)}她們的「日常」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 19點是攝影棚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.83,0:02:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥小姐 這個我一起跟去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 這邊也有事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,655)\fs40}明顯人手不夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長說近期就會增加人手了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安 我是秋月律子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在765PRO擔任製作人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.12,0:03:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這間事務所有多少在籍偶像？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.75,0:03:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中大部分人都是半年前剛剛出道的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都還是新手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.13,0:03:34.38,Default_P,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說秋月小姐原來也是偶像來著…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.63,0:03:37.35,Default_P,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不再作為偶像開展活動了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我想保密來著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.14,0:03:43.14,Default_P,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.28,0:03:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便 你從誰那聽來這事的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.10,0:03:46.86,Default_P,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是高木社長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.51,0:03:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.79,0:03:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 嘴上沒把鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.21,0:03:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我現在作為新人製作人在努力喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.05,0:03:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 也終於拿到駕照了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.85,0:03:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們在幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.94,0:04:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正在接受採訪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.52,0:04:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 妳們兩個也來好好打個招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes Sir！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.50,0:04:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙海亞美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.73,0:04:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙海真美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.21,0:04:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐 也問亞美一點問題嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓真美也拍一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 別搗亂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.46,0:04:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.78,0:04:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次又怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.38,0:04:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈姆藏不知道跑哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.90,0:04:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快出來呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊 吵吵鬧鬧的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈姆藏不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.87,0:04:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為看起來挺好吃的 所以我不小心把哈姆藏的飯吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後哈姆藏那傢伙就生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.45,0:04:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿妳沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.26,0:04:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈姆藏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.38,0:04:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:04:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.28,0:05:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿響 我們幫妳抓牠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.74,0:05:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要抓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.48,0:05:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.69,0:05:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我道歉還不行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼 有什麼東西在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.22,0:05:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪…哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟑螂 討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.94,0:05:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 阿真
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.11,0:05:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有男人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟑螂討厭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪步 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.99,0:05:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪步 冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 誰來把蟑螂弄走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.46,0:05:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪步 不能在熱水房地板上挖坑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.37,0:05:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個 快點把蟑螂…把蟑螂趕出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 哈姆藏是倉鼠啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.77,0:05:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？哈姆藏？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.45,0:06:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳上當了 真
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊織妳又來這套
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.83,0:06:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 上當的人才是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.79,0:06:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼理論啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.01,0:06:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.62,0:06:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真 伊織 攝影機正在拍喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.35,0:06:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電視臺的採訪…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？這個一直都在拍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 妳早點說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我叫水瀨伊織 請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.10,0:06:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈姆藏 你已經被包圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.31,0:06:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄吧 趕快出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.06,0:06:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 哈姆藏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.74,0:06:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 大家吵吵鬧鬧的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是熱鬧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個要多少錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.78,0:07:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看容量大小吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會隨大小變化嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.92,0:07:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,655)\fs40}這算是小的了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容量指的是記憶體啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真難懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的 妳看連我都明白啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我估計沒戲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.94,0:07:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 這是化妝占卜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.89,0:07:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 本月的工作運是1顆星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.62,0:07:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過戀愛運有3顆星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.54,0:07:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.49,0:07:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可思議的占卜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個真的準嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.26,0:07:49.26,Default_P,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們相信占卜嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.33,0:07:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 如果寫的是好事就相信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴音妳的占卜結果怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:07:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.14,0:08:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信人生需要靠自己去開闢命運
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開闢命運？也許真是如此啊 貴音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.93,0:08:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,655)\fs40}哈姆藏在哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.77,0:08:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑進這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.77,0:08:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我乖乖束手就擒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.24,0:08:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑進美希美希這裡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈姆藏也是男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.11,0:08:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 哈姆藏你這個色鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.97,0:08:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈姆藏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.31,0:08:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.64,0:08:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,655)\fs40}我吃了哈姆藏的飯對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.29,0:08:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希美希 有攝影機喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.19,0:08:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說幾句嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.30,0:08:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星井美希 初三來著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.14,0:08:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.97,0:08:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？就這些？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太快了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.24,0:08:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有胸部很大喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.59,0:08:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 美希美希
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.04,0:09:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是多睡有利於發育嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這裡人手不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 有些聽不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.46,0:09:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您再說一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.37,0:09:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 大家給我適可而止吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.04,0:09:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.65,0:09:21.65,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,450)\fs95\pos(519,510)}職 業：
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.94,0:09:21.65,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,450)\fs95\pos(750,510)}偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.33,0:09:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 雖然還有很多事情不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.92,0:09:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過像這樣一點點的漸漸進步就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？美希做得很棒吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.51,0:10:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我對體力很有自信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.36,0:10:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我特別想磨練舞技
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在電視的歌唱節目和大舞臺上帥氣的跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.62,0:10:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菊地君女孩子中很有人氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為很男孩子氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.21,0:10:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是這個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.36,0:10:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我變成這樣都怪老爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我要是想女孩子氣一點他就會來妨礙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.99,0:10:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,655)\fs40}真…真
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.16,0:10:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天我得打破老爸那堵牆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.83,0:10:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看好了！老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.39,0:10:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 萩原雪歩小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.44,0:10:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我不擅長跟男人對話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.77,0:10:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼要當偶像啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.43,0:10:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 因為我沒有什麼能自豪的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.09,0:10:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻想要成為偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.34,0:10:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…是不是做夢做過頭了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算妳這麼問我也…對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.66,0:11:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想矯正自己畏畏縮縮的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.71,0:11:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是試鏡機會也是朋友給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我完全不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.78,0:11:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…聽不清您在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.89,0:11:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 雪歩 回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.41,0:11:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.69,0:11:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.75,0:11:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是天海春香 請看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.88,0:11:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 當律子小姐抽不出身的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.11,0:11:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會像這樣來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 請收下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:35.00,Default_P,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是兼職製作人這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.15,0:11:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不是這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我頂多就是幫幫忙而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.07,0:11:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.98,0:11:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去趕下一個場子了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.26,0:11:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攝影師先生 春香就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.14,0:11:50.01,Default_P,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:53.23,Default_P,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了你了…啥的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.80,0:11:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人拜託了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.35,0:11:55.98,Default_P,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈…哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.58,0:11:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就一起加油吧 喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:01.11,Default_P,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔…喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.30,0:12:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青之鳥 如若幸福…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:18.12,Default_P,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳對於歌抱有什麼想法呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論什麼歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.56,0:12:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都想認真對待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.94,0:12:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我做不到的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.56,0:12:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是對於歌還是對於聽眾都是件很失禮的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:30.97,Default_P,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很喜歡唱歌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.36,0:12:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 因為我除了歌唱就一無所有了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.55,0:12:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒時間玩樂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.93,0:12:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 抱歉 這樣可以了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.21,0:12:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想集中精力練習
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.40,0:12:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我就那樣跳了出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.32,0:12:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大喊「給我等等」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:13:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是765PRO的四條貴音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.46,0:13:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪裡人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問我是哪裡人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.96,0:13:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 這是最高機密
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.66,0:13:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以無法告知
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.18,0:13:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳真是有意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:20.52,Default_P,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的試鏡 挺成功的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.64,0:13:22.77,Default_P,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「是哪裡人為最高機密」是故意博取歡迎嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博取…歡迎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.84,0:13:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您指的是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.85,0:13:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不喜歡別人單純因為興趣而詢問我的出身而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是誰都會有一個或百個秘密的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.57,0:13:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那請自我介紹一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.23,0:13:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.95,0:13:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不對 我叫我那霸響
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.40,0:13:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級擅長跳舞並且最喜歡動物了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:14:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家裡有養倉鼠 蛇 花栗鼠 兔子 狗 貓 鱷魚 豬 鼯鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.60,0:14:03.60,Default_P,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,養這麼多動物不會很辛苦嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.26,0:14:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人越多越熱鬧才好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.14,0:14:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是我可愛的弟弟妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次哈姆藏逃走的時候才更加辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.43,0:14:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.82,0:14:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在…在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.58,0:14:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只說了寵物的話題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.50,0:14:29.46,Default_P,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試鏡失敗了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.78,0:14:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 今天是雜誌專屬封面偶像的試鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.99,0:14:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但很遺憾…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.96,0:14:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易從律子小姐那裡得到了建議
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.77,0:14:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備了決勝POSE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.76,0:14:42.77,Default_P,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順帶一提是什麼樣的POSE？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.39,0:14:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是這種感覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是對不起律子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:52.65,Default_P,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(793,0)}加入765PRO的契機是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.44,0:14:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 短大畢業後不知不覺就來應聘了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:15:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前既沒有唱過歌也沒跳過舞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.91,0:15:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想著大概努力個五年應該就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.82,0:15:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在才過了半年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.52,0:15:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後的路還長著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 比起這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.46,0:15:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 這裡是哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.26,0:15:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:27.23,Default_P,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是水瀨小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說您家不是那個有名的水瀨財閥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.35,0:15:30.48,Default_P,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,545)}為什麼決定成為偶像呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.05,0:15:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親和哥哥們確實如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.83,0:15:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我想靠自己的雙手去抓住點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.88,0:15:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這個事務所也是自己來應聘面試的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.24,0:15:43.83,Default_P,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,545)}我還聽說是因為社長被熟人拜託了要接受妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.12,0:15:50.00,Default_P,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那隻兔子是？我看妳一直都抱著對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.73,0:15:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.36,0:15:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子可是有正經名字的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.13,0:15:56.67,Default_P,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.17,0:15:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:16:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊織的小兔子叫什麼名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.95,0:16:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏露露·多娜提魯多18世
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.12,0:16:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽上去像甜甜圈一樣很好吃的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.06,0:16:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 別跟甜甜圈混為一談啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.98,0:16:13.23,Default_P,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼有個問題想問高槻小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.27,0:16:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.48,0:16:15.86,Default_P,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳有什麼值得自豪的地方嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我是6個兄弟姐妹中的老大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.22,0:16:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家還是挺窮的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.31,0:16:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維持家計很辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.97,0:16:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我會照顧弟弟妹妹們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.61,0:16:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用超市的賤賣品和限時減價
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精打細算的買東西這方面值得自豪…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.67,0:16:36.38,Default_P,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,545)}不是指這方面 是想請妳說說自己作為偶像的賣點(汗)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.15,0:16:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.05,0:16:48.68,Default_P,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…難道不是這個開朗的性格嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.88,0:16:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像完全想不出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.58,0:16:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開朗的性格就是賣點？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.42,0:16:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 總覺得那個賣字很不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(854,505)\c&H42973F&\bord0\fs60}超級幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有賺到了的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.06,0:17:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就以每天就要大拍賣的氣勢加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.91,0:17:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後把這個數字代入
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:18.34,Default_P,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時兼顧學校和偶像活動兩方面很辛苦吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.75,0:17:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不管哪方面都很開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.51,0:17:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 真美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.66,0:17:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開心的事情越多越覺得賺到了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.25,0:17:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要兩人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.22,0:17:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦的事情也可以分擔一半
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.41,0:17:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要大家在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有開心的事情對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.81,0:17:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這些作業完全不開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.27,0:17:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.38,0:17:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.30,0:17:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Byebye
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.91,0:17:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就再見了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像要下雨了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花會凋謝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.96,0:17:59.09,Default_P,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為偶像的條件是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:18:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.11,0:18:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是永不言棄這點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不需要懷有無法實現的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.69,0:18:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是需要一直擁有可以實現夢想的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然由我來說有點那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.10,0:18:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我真的很期待她們作為偶像的成長喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:21.11,Default_P,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很期待律子小姐作為偶像的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.40,0:18:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(267,446)\bord0}765Production社長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.78,0:18:26.53,Default_P,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼最後拜託高木社長說一句吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.99,0:18:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.69,0:18:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律子君已經把所有東西都說了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:33.04,Default_P,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:37.59,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,450)\fs90\pos(640,510)}提問
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.64,0:18:40.80,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,450)\pos(640,450)}對妳來說「偶像」是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.91,0:18:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣輕飄飄 光鮮亮麗的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.78,0:18:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是有一天也能成為那樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 因為我對自己沒什麼信心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:18:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要是能成為不一樣的自己就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.52,0:19:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得超開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.79,0:19:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯 真想快點多在電視上露露臉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.34,0:19:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 盡可能地多給家裡賺點錢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.30,0:19:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想給父母減輕點負擔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.27,0:19:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還用說！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.62,0:19:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是為了讓大家承認我伊織醬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.47,0:19:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣作為偶像而努力的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會被誰發現到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.66,0:19:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得去賺大家的飼料錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.96,0:19:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個也是最高機密
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.61,0:19:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為美希我不怎麼喜歡吃苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.34,0:19:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以如果能以輕鬆萬歲的態度去當偶像就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.99,0:19:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.58,0:19:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夢想…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.10,0:19:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是憧憬喔 從小開始的憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.46,0:19:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說沒有痛苦的事那是騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.05,0:19:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這個夢想才剛剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以現在不會考慮除此之外的任何事情喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.98,0:20:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,450)\pos(640,450)}毫無變化一味流逝的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.98,0:20:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,450)\pos(640,450)}漸漸開始有了改變
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.19,0:20:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,450)\pos(640,450)}帶著少女們的思緒……
